  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare parallel-group effects between 4 months and 12 months
      post-transplantation 2 values of target residual concentrations of Advagraf on vascular
      parameters in de novo renal transplant patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
